Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "Gra-Grandpa, I'm back. The city's been secretly throwing out lots of weird trash in the past few days. I collected them all and traded them for some rye bread!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "It's not a lot... But we won't have to starve for the next few days!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Old Man', 3: "Karen, Karen you're back! Grandpa is not hungry, so little Karen can have all the bread.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Old Man', 3: "Oh! That must've been the snoring of those pesky rats in the house!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Old Man', 3: 'Right! Karen! Come, come. Move this to the grounds outside!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "It's a bit heavy... What is this, Grandpa?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Old Man', 3: "I modified it myself. I'm going to give it to you as a secret birthday present on your birthday!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Old Man', 3: 'Come help Grandpa move it out and test it!', 4: '2'}
